{"tid":331243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊招募 自7年來最高投考人數","createTime":"2017-07-22T03:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T12:50:12.000Z","uid":22791,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b50be401a02f20d3c4fb9126b8caaf3dcfb4feb","tid":331243,"uid":22791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:44:08.000Z","msg":"警隊今日（七月二十二日）在警察總部舉辦夏季「警察招募日」，招募見習督察、警員及輔警警員。<br />\n<br />\n今次招募日共收到超過２　６００份申請，比去年同期上升百分之三點四；當中超過１　８００人投考警員，是自二○一○年以來的最高投考人數。<br />\n  <br />\n香港人真係好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口裡說不身體卻很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑警萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201707/22/P2017072200363.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201707%2F22%2FP2017072200363.htm&d=%2Ftg94tjo1WDcL9EzSfBCB5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1e019184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201707/22/P2017072200363.htm</a>"},{"pid":"3b0edf6815d048fa3938500c64312fc4d2acdbe4","tid":331243,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e260c6bb0b0bbff343f040b38bb673c4ea2ccc51","tid":331243,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:45:45.000Z","msg":"口嫌體正直<br />\n中國人特色<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1555e65ed78059f8834b839e06de2f58218553ed","tid":331243,"uid":55888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017